properties.areaDesc: Southern Sacramento Valley; Northern San Joaquin Valley
properties.headline: Dense Fog Advisory issued January 7 at 10:03AM PST until January 7 at 12:00PM PST by NWS Sacramento CA
properties.description:
...Areas of Dense Fog in the Central Valley...

.Areas of dense fog in the Southern Sacramento Valley and Northern
San Joaquin Valley will continue until midday. Use caution while
driving.

* WHAT...Visibility below one quarter mile in dense fog.

* WHERE...Southern Sacramento Valley and Northern San Joaquin
Valley Counties.

* WHEN...Until noon PST today.

* IMPACTS...Hazardous driving conditions due to low visibility.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...Use low beam headlights. If possible, delay
driving until early this afternoon.
properties.instruction:
If driving, slow down, use your headlights, and leave plenty of
distance ahead of you.

NWSheadline: DENSE FOG ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL NOON PST TODAY
